			<h2 class="title">Louis L. Biro Law Library</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="clear"></div>

		<div class="grid_12">
			
			<h3>Reference Services</h3>
            
			<p>The Louis L. Biro Law Library Reference Services serves the UIC Law community by providing dynamic guidance, outreach, and instruction regarding the information resources central to the education and research mission of the law school. Reference Librarians respond to the immediate research needs of our patrons and develop our collection, skills, and services in anticipation of the changing legal information environment.</p>

			<h5>Reference Hours</h5>

			<!-- Pass in the calendar from an <iframe> -->
			<div id="">
				<iframe width="700px" height="160px" frameborder="0" src="refhrsource.php" scrolling="no"></iframe>
			</div>
